title: Ep. - 261 - REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW YORK AND SELLING SUNSET
description:
Michael Byrne appeared with a sweater tied around his neck and holding a martini in this season of Real Housewives of New York’s most entertaining dinner episode. He talks about what it is was like to witness the scene from the sidelines.

 

John Raphael is the host of Wannabe: A Pop Culture Podcast and content creator for A Brit and a Yank. Kate asks him to explain why Selling Sunset is a must watch show to binge.
